1.0.1 2026-04-30
  - Added BEP044-compliant stimuli/ structure (BIDS-spec PR #2022):
      * stimuli/stimuli.tsv (16,740 rows: 16,540 train + 200 test)
        with columns stimulus_id, type, license, copyright, description,
        URL, filename, present.
      * stimuli/stimuli.json describing the columns above and the
        events.tsv "tot_img_number" ↔ "stimulus_id" mapping convention.
      * BIDS-named copies of every image at
        stimuli/training_images/<concept>/stim-train<NNNNN>_image.jpg
        stimuli/test_images/<concept>/stim-test<NNN>_image.jpg
        deduplicated against the originals via git-annex (same SHA256E
        key, no extra S3 storage).
  - Added code/align_stimuli.py: StimulusAligner helper that resolves
    events.tsv rows to stimulus image paths.
  - Added code/build_stim_bids.py: idempotent script that produced the
    BEP044 layout from the existing zips and image_metadata.npy.
  - Added code/smoke_test_braindecode.py: end-to-end alignment proof
    using braindecode.datasets.BIDSDataset and mne.Epochs.
  - Added .github/workflows/bids-validation.yml and version-check.yml
    so PRs against this dataset are gated by the BIDS validator and a
    Version-bump check.
  - Added Version field ("1.0.0" → "1.0.1") to dataset_description.json
    (the field was previously absent).

1.0.0 2026-04-11
  - Initial release. Conversion of THINGS-EEG2 source EEG and
    behavioural .mat files to BIDS-EEG; original BrainVision files
    preserved under sourcedata/, authors' preprocessed data under
    derivatives/, image stimuli under stimuli/.
